      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large pot with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
