      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 375ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[500ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
