    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>sliced garlic </strong>and <strong>dried basil </strong>to the pot with your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>chopped olives </strong>and <strong>capers</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
