            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato stock </strong>and your <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>to the pot with your <strong>tortiglioni </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 12-15 min, stirring occasionally, until the pasta is cooked through and the sauce has thickened</p>",
