        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the tortiglioni is cooking, chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
